<pre>indexing and we might be getting somewhere.</pre><pre>&nbsp;</pre><pre>&nbsp;</pre><pre>&nbsp;</pre><pre>&nbsp;</pre><pre>On Mon, Jul 16, 2012 at 6:25 PM, Pablo A. Destéfanis</pre><pre><a href="mailto:pdestefanis@...">&lt;pdestefanis@...&gt;</a> wrote:</pre><blockquote style="margin-top:5.0pt;margin-bottom:5.0pt"><pre>I agree with Emmanuel, and let me add:</pre><pre>&nbsp;</pre><pre>&nbsp;</pre><pre>&nbsp;</pre><pre>·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; While PostGIS is excellent, quite a lot can be done with MySQL’s</pre>
